</bibRefCitation>
). It grows on dry hills, in desert or semidesert steppes, dry river valleys, or at forest margins at altitudes of 
<quantity id="4CDB9B40433FFFE367C7FEF9C150FE80" box="[136,293,266,293]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.85" metricValueMax="4.6" metricValueMin="1.1" pageId="7" pageNumber="80" unit="m" value="2850.0" valueMax="4600.0" valueMin="1100.0">1100–4600 m</quantity>
