</taxonomicName>
, under the name of 
<taxonomicName id="4C234D26433FFFE367E9FC28C1B9FC51" authorityName="Ling" authorityYear="1988" baseAuthorityName="Pampanini" box="[166,460,986,1013]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="7" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="argyrophylla" variety="brevis">
<emphasis id="B957EAB7433FFFE367E9FC28C0C2FC50" box="[166,183,987,1013]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B957EAB7433FFFE3678BFC29C121FC51" box="[196,340,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">argyrophylla</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B957EAB7433FFFE366C6FC29C1B9FC51" box="[393,460,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">brevis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in Ruoqiang county in 
<collectingRegion id="49E7F847433FFFE36598FC29C349FC51" box="[727,828,986,1012]" country="China" name="Xinjiang Uygur" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">Xinjiang</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3347635433FFFE36409FC29C3F9FC51" box="[838,908,986,1012]" name="China" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">China</collectingCountry>
, without citing any specimen. However, we have been unable to trace any specimen referable to this variety (or 
<taxonomicName id="4C234D26433FFFE36477FC0CC3ECFBBD" authorityName="Pampanini" authorityYear="1938" box="[824,921,1022,1049]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Artemisia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="7" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brevis">
<emphasis id="B957EAB7433FFFE36477FC0CC3ECFBBD" box="[824,921,1022,1049]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="80">A. brevis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) from this county in the major relevant Chinese herbaria, including HNWP, NWTC, PE, WUK, and XJBI. Further research and filed work are needed to verify the distribution of this species in Ruoqiang.
</paragraph>
